==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Kurdish
<hw>Kurd"ish</hw>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>The language of the Kurds;
it is related to Farsi, the modern Iranian language.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>Koordish</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kurilian</ent>⟦br⟧
